{"tid":2265010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"襲警案被告骨折  目擊者：警瞄頭棍毆","createTime":"2020-10-31T05:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T07:25:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"66a19140c7f2faad04a9a26c108db560aa57b5be","tid":2265010,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T05:53:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201031/2H6IUFCXRRFCVEIYOGZYIA4XUU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201031%2F2H6IUFCXRRFCVEIYOGZYIA4XUU%2F&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=c7faa747\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201031%2F2H6IUFCXRRFCVEIYOGZYIA4XUU%2F&h=e5e6c6fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201031/2H6IUFCXRRFCVEIYOGZYIA4XUU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n襲警案被告骨折 <br />\n目擊者：警瞄頭棍毆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XegigPUk4_5kNTpNtBKX9wAOOYI=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SR2P2ZGJJVHYJGOZQXA5LLY6Q4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXegigPUk4_5kNTpNtBKX9wAOOYI%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSR2P2ZGJJVHYJGOZQXA5LLY6Q4.jpg&h=61c337da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告羅鎮傑被指企圖搶奪警司胡椒噴霧，被控襲警罪。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年9月港島「自由行」示威期間，一名聽障男生被指企圖搶奪警司的胡椒噴霧，被控襲警罪，案件續審。早前三名警方證人均供稱看不見同僚向被告揮警棍，但有市民昨供稱，當日目擊多名警員「瞄頭」揮警棍毆打被告近十下，他欲阻止不果，反被其他警員毆打。辯方昨引述醫療報告，證實被告事後左肋骨前方兩節骨折、右肋骨移位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖阻止反被打<br />\n<br />\n.............................................<br />\n<br />\n目擊事發經過的市民鄺耀熊（38歲）昨供稱，當日由鵝頸橋回家，走到銅鑼灣港鐵站C出口外，看見被告遭約四名警員用警棍由上至下揮打，「我好肯定警察係瞄住佢個頭嚟打，我下意識覺得會出事，所以就過去阻止」。惟鄺隨即遭其他警員拉走制止，「俾佢打咗陣，同向我噴咗好多胡椒噴霧」。後來鄺與被告一同被帶到銅鑼灣港鐵站下層，然後前住北角警署，其間有警員向鄺指出，「頭先你要救嘅人就係呢個人」。<br />\n<br />\n辯方引述事發翌日被告的醫療報告，證實被告有兩節左肋骨前方骨折，右肋骨輕微移位，身體多處有瘀傷及擦傷。案件下周二續審。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC291/20"},{"pid":"475cdb23fef520b3e50e851204018b5ab3d20db6","tid":2265010,"uid":86204,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T05:58:06.000Z","msg":"擺到明係被告頭同身故意撞向棍<br />\n目擊者明顯造謠！"},{"pid":"a96457ab3a3ccc6e7b01882f2c46847c8ab98223","tid":2265010,"uid":113000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T06:35:59.000Z","msg":"嚴重傷人仲可以老屈人受害者<br />\n<br />\n得香港先做得出"},{"pid":"556a5d2c0e09ea507f3138fc99e2f1d6047c740e","tid":2265010,"uid":59522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a96457ab3a3ccc6e7b01882f2c46847c8ab98223","tid":2265010,"uid":113000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T06:35:59.000Z","msg":"嚴重傷人仲可以老屈人受害者<br />\n<br />\n得香港先做得出"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T06:48:47.000Z","msg":"講個笑話你聽<br />\n法治"},{"pid":"46cf64f3062d810104efc093647b1cfb9b96a7d8","tid":2265010,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"556a5d2c0e09ea507f3138fc99e2f1d6047c740e","tid":2265010,"uid":59522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a96457ab3a3ccc6e7b01882f2c46847c8ab98223","tid":2265010,"uid":113000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T06:35:59.000Z","msg":"嚴重傷人仲可以老屈人受害者<br />\n<br />\n得香港先做得出"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T06:48:47.000Z","msg":"講個笑話你聽<br />\n法治"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:09:45.000Z","msg":"錯<br />\n係香港法治/OMDB"},{"pid":"2c3f62fc7e407751f35c0b380c0aed0fb77f517b","tid":2265010,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4008e9a6bd4d78056e365e4003be0e5ac49f2d0e","tid":2265010,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:22:44.000Z","msg":"希望唔係狗官"},{"pid":"416b5b4413263c30eaaaf660dc752e88fe9c2ebe","tid":2265010,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:25:40.000Z","msg":"市民瘋狂撞向警棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}